:#  Function        LocalPath.Add/LocalPath.Remove                            #
:#                  MasterPath.Get/MasterPath.Add/MasterPath.Remove           #
:#                                                                            #
:#  Description     Path management routines			              #
:#                                                                            #
:#  Note                                                                      #
:#                                                                            #
:#  History                                                                   #
:#   2020-03-12 JFL Copied from paths.bat.                                    #
